Parliament, Tuesday, 02 July 2019 – The Portfolio Committee on Justice and Correctional Services will tomorrow receive a political overview from the Minister of Justice and Correctional Services. The committee will further receive a briefing from the Department of Justice and Constitutional Development on its Annual Performance Plan and Budget. Details are as follows: Date: Wednesday, 03 July 2019
	Time: 9:30 am
	Venue: Committee Room 2, Ground Floor, 90 Plein Street Building ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES For media enquiries or interviews, please contact the committee’s Media Officer: Name: Rajaa Azzakani (Ms)
	Tel: 021 403 8437
	Cell: 081 703 9542
